skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: stuart guide
des: Explore the city with the Stuart Guide. Whether this is your first trip or you have visited many times before there is always something interesting to discover in Stuart. Begin by opening the Stuart guide and asking for an overview. You can also ask for the top five things to do or for an attraction. For a complete list of options ask the guide for help.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
